{"tid":732562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世盃星球人】軒達臣不敗「巨肺」","createTime":"2018-07-07T04:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T07:48:19.000Z","uid":7715,"like":69,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"06c64d82c2e2197017ab4a5de25c07848e149f65","tid":732562,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://greatrednorth.files.wordpress.com/2013/09/run-hendo-run.gif?w=634&amp;h=266\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatrednorth.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F09%2Frun-hendo-run.gif%3Fw%3D634%26h%3D266&h=f04f79cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=88483d39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦中場佐敦軒達臣雖然射失12碼，但觀感上和從數據觀之，其位置在國家隊依然是不可或缺。<br />\n<br />\n今年28歲的利物浦中場猛將佐敦軒達臣（Jordan Henderson），無疑是英格蘭表現最穩定的球員之一，翻查資料，其上陣28場的比賽，球隊悉數保持不敗，絕對是三獅福將，難怪修夫基雖然沒有讓他肩負隊長重任，但仍器重有加。<br />\n<br />\n軒達臣最近在國家隊上陣的28場，取得22勝6和佳績，並成為國家史上最長不敗紀錄的球員，即使16強對哥倫比亞時射失12碼，但球隊仍能打破12碼必輸的魔咒，殺入8強面對瑞典。<br />\n<br />\n「巨肺」軒達臣跑上跑落，助攻助守體力充沛，踢法無私，覆蓋面極大，重要性不言而喻，16強射失12碼後，他已公開道歉，並指永遠欠救出12碼的隊友比克福特一份恩情，鏡頭前的他，也差點流下男兒淚，果然是真性情。"},{"pid":"956fe44d641e513e13382a2ebd81d364e8df63ab","tid":732562,"uid":7715,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d8156e54dd86c7d2dd896f266dfe19dcf29eac54","tid":732562,"uid":36497,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407560048ab594ddb08ecd821b526d87d4228be4","tid":732562,"uid":71398,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"軒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2932c30ddda47a514201f37defef35ba6dcb359","tid":732562,"uid":7715,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"cit